
**on alohemy it is a meditation in which the sense of unit is aware of the differentiations between the knower and the known so it is the one in which the mind is in a lesser degree it consists of two kind vis sathanu and tvisanu as mentioned in the above stanzas**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   சவிகற்பசமாதி
